776
00:59:12,010 --> 00:59:13,580
<font color="yellow">Jadi kau bisa menarik semuanya keluar.</font>

777
00:59:24,380 --> 00:59:26,450
<font color="yellow">Satu, dua, tiga.</font>

778
00:59:27,610 --> 00:59:28,950
<font color="yellow">Yang mana?</font>

779
00:59:55,610 --> 00:59:56,850
<font color="yellow">Kurasa kau sedang bersenang-senang...</font>

780
00:59:56,910 --> 00:59:58,980
<font color="yellow">Saat karyawanmu bekerja sampai mati.</font>

781
01:00:01,010 --> 01:00:02,450
<font color="yellow">Apakah itu tidak terjadi hari ini?</font>

